{"tid":935540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦包攬印特區護照 年搵三千萬","createTime":"2018-12-10T05:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T12:40:11.000Z","uid":2625,"like":370,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac23ab7792801e290ea839897cf20e0c842193a","tid":935540,"uid":2625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong>2015年04月17日</strong></strong><br />\n本刊上星期踢爆中聯辦迂迴持有聯合出版集團九成九股份，公然違反《基本法》營運書店及出版事業，干預香港商業活動。記者追查的過程中發現，聯合出版還擁有一家「中華商務安全印務」，印製香港特區護照。不少申請護照的市民均大感嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n單是特區護照，該公司每年獲特區政府最少三千萬元合約，政府亦有另外兩種証件，透過非公開招標批出合約，予中華商務安全印務印製，由○七年起計，合約總值超過六千萬元。究竟政府有否公開招標批出印製特區護照？入境處並無正無回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20150417/184150?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20150417%2F184150%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=3VF6E2gJR1D7OfX8qt8MeMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=588aad08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20150417%2F184150%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ac039556\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20150417/184150?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"36256523d0ce0b8de0af448cf19f01b78576a72f","tid":935540,"uid":2625,"like":283,"dislike":0,"score":283,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"政府唔洗解釋啦? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fae9adfc6fefd860ecaed70fd3140bcd89add2c","tid":935540,"uid":77196,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"quote":{"pid":"36256523d0ce0b8de0af448cf19f01b7857